Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a captain at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not live on in disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you guys\Nby slashing you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow that…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as our destination lies\Nbeyond where you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crooked sword attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right-Angle Flying Bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…Bone…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He discerned it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold Hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated Ship-Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he\Nfollowed the sea train
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the detached cars\Nin this storm…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your justice is deep, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we also shoulder\Nall sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss! You're the very definition\Nof "all bark but no bite."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys being\Ndeceived by that woman, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the lowest of the low,\Nwho lived one betrayal after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and survived until today\Nin the underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decoupage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you add your last\Nwords to them while you're at it, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where on earth\Ndid you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish taking\Ncare of the ramen guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suddenly become noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the soldiers for this escort mission\Nwere annihilated after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't expect much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who\Nkidnapped Robin-chan, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They use strange martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably that CP9 newbie\Nthat Corgy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a Four Power\NMaster named Nero or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me a fighting genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y… You must be Rob Lucci, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I didn't\Nintroduce myself sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him first and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're capturing Franky alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you let your feelings take\Ncontrol and lost sight of our mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run…? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:05.24,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now\Nlet's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.66,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.04,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through\Nour clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:16.33,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.82,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.21,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:37.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,there's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.63,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:48.41,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through\Nthe rainbow-colored wind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.70,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.50,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey\Nfraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:59.42,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most\Nwill be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.42,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.47,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:10.64,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!\NNow let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.18,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.56,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:21.69,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:25.40,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up\Nthe pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.70,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map\Nleading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.12,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:37.47,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag--\Ntogether, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.79,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scramble over Robin!\NA Cunning Plan by Sogeking!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run…? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you who does\Neverything halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is unfit for CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you've mastered all Six Powers,\Nyou aren't superhuman, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inform our chief later…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the newbie was so\Nweak that he was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are supposed\Nto be working for justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tell which side is evil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officials from the World\NGovernment sure are ill-mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my duty, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sense of smell\Nis absolute, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take off that cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W… Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man\Nwho hails from the island of snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can\Nget away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the resolution\Nof a man who is willing to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L… L… Lucci-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have to ask\Nwhy you are here, intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the way you opened the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't seem like\Nyou have a lot of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm ill-bred, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about Nico Robin…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too big of an issue for you\Nguys to get yourselves involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people in the world who\Nwere born under an unlucky star...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who are better off\Ndead for everyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose there exists a devil that\Nwould burn the world to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person who\Ncan raise this devil
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is an innocent girl\Nwho's only eight years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…don't you think…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should kill\Nthis girl for everyone's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you\Nthat is Nico Robin's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a real criminal now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it started simple like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her existence itself was a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can make others happy\Nonly by disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the misfortune she carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she should've died 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad that this\Nwoman will be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Government\Nwill probably spend years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…squeezing out all\Nof Nico Robin's knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,experience and intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much agony she'll experience\Nbefore she dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just watch and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Seriously! Seriously! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to all the trouble\Nof getting in from outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even brought\Nthat official down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She indeed bears a resemblance to\Nthe picture in the wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring these guys down\Nright away, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I explain, you guys\Njust won't get it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I explain, you guys\Njust won't get it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detach car #3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment will decide the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Franky get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke… Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a petty thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he said we're turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we should get\Nready to turn back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! When we came this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Robin!\NWhat about Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're we gonna do\Nabout them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that guy thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we turning back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us why!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was telling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that frog that jumped\Non the railway to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit! Ribbit! Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yokozuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that huge frog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside, frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got Robin back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nthat sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that we suddenly switched\Nto a "Running Away" strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smoke screen is so stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that people wouldn't normally\Nthink of using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we can achieve our goal\Nwithout fighting scary guys like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't know if things\Nare gonna be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down\Nuntil the cars are really far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thorny whips?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna use the whips\Nto cross over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They pulled us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smoke screen?\NWhat a worthless thing to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it couldn't\Nhave worked after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill any Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Robin-chan\Nat all costs, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm…? Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…make you let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is his body so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that they use\Nstrange martial arts, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got quite a heavy kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body almost got broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno, don't take him lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a bounty on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's one of their main forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed that,\Nyou damn jerks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, R-Robin!\NHey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow… Wh-What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocho Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times\Ndo I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez… Why are all of you\Nbeing so stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even towards your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a perfect chance to run, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't expect that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking sides\Nwith them in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't bear to watch\Nthose guys act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not when there's a team that couldn't\Ngo back even if they wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've joined up with Straw Hat,\Nget back to town somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting\Nlike that at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to rescue you\Nknowing all the circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just do something about the\NGovernment's attack, Buster Call,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be a reason that\Nyou have to obey them, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Buster Call is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…indeed the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:23.40,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.22,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:33.25,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:36.92,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:44.09,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.42,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.11,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:56.81,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.70,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:05.39,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Let Robin-chan go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!\NWhy aren't you saying anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, you're still hiding\Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pirate cannot leave their group\Nwithout their captain's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Robin…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believe in Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Judicial Island!\NFull View of Enies Lobby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
